{"tid":756190,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"「大媽」影相阻步操　被英御林軍推開","createTime":"2018-07-26T00:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T02:15:43.000Z","uid":81228,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"30153a1dbd0506871f00a6edf098a6e47745eec0","tid":756190,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T00:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2120000/2123220/026_02_a_20180726_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2120000%2F2123220%2F026_02_a_20180726_L.jpg&h=6dbf88dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名亞裔中年女遊客越過了圍繩，背向御林軍希望與其合照。<br />\n<br />\n到英國旅遊，觀看御林軍步操是其中一個熱門行程。社交平台近日流傳影片，一名亞裔中年女遊客越過圍繩，阻礙御林軍步操前進，結果被一手推開，她向前撲並大聲尖叫，幸未有跌倒。<br />\n<br />\n影片可見，一名亞裔中年女遊客越過了圍繩，背向御林軍希望與其合照。不料阻礙了御林軍的步操路綫，御林軍隨即將她大力推開，大媽慘叫一聲差點跌倒，其男伴將她抓住，而御林軍則沒有理會，繼續步操。英國國防部回應，御林軍很榮幸各地民眾來觀賞步操儀式，但呼籲遊客要留在指定範圍，切勿超越圍繩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2123220/%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E3%80%8D%E5%BD%B1%E7%9B%B8%E9%98%BB%E6%AD%A5%E6%93%8D%20%E8%A2%AB%E8%8B%B1%E5%BE%A1%E6%9E%97%E8%BB%8D%E6%8E%A8%E9%96%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2123220%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E6%2593%258D%2520%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25BE%25A1%25E6%259E%2597%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%258E%25A8%25E9%2596%258B&d=jlsdZ6hoUHRkzPCMuPZ9aC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=126945b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2123220/%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E3%80%8D%E5%BD%B1%E7%9B%B8%E9%98%BB%E6%AD%A5%E6%93%8D%20%E8%A2%AB%E8%8B%B1%E5%BE%A1%E6%9E%97%E8%BB%8D%E6%8E%A8%E9%96%8B</a>"},{"pid":"7c6be849183574745d29e93938ef44cf92fad653","tid":756190,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T01:55:54.000Z","msg":"自己擺黎賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494cfe236435ce89728969ce578128aa6865e489","tid":756190,"uid":6694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T01:57:10.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079076838183889bcc98d71a9d8024ea2b4dbd7d","tid":756190,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:15:43.000Z","msg":"次次有事就亞裔"}]}